---
title: "US57 — Review expert applications"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertsApprovalScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ReviewExpertVerification
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: open pending application + documents
  alt approve
    B->>C: approve(expertId)
    C->>G: verification_status = verified, role = expert
    B-->>A: expert goes live
  else reject
    B->>C: reject(expertId, reason)
    C->>G: verification_status = rejected
    B-->>A: applicant notified
  end
